title: Week 3 Preview
itunes:title: Week 3 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal spin through every week 3 upcoming game and what to expect. The guys went 0-4 last week on their locks and are determined to make up for it this time. Josh Rosen was named starting quarterback for the Dolphins, will this change their chances against the Patriots?
